          dt.col-sm-2.text-sm-end 08/13/2021
          dd.col-sm-10 The #[a(href="/program.html") preliminary program] is available.

          dt.col-sm-2.text-sm-end 07/29/2021
          dd.col-sm-10.text-danger #[strong.text-danger Please Note: the conference will be virtual only].

          dt.col-sm-2.text-sm-end 07/06/2021
